-- 
Manchester City Targets Fabregas, Modric, the People Reports

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-05-22T11:48:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-22/manchester-city-targets-fabregas-modric-the-people-reports.html
Manchester City  will offer a U.K.
record 58 million pounds ($94 million) for Arsenal captain Cesc Fabregas, with Tottenham’s Luka Modric also a target,  the People
reported.   Arsenal wants 60 million pounds for the 24-year-old
Fabregas, who would prefer a move to Spanish soccer champion
Barcelona, the newspaper said, without citing anyone.  City hopes to beat archrival Manchester United to the
signing of Modric and may also compete with the Premier League
champion for Inter Milan’s Wesley Sneijder and Aston Villa’s
Ashley Young, the People reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 James Cone  in London at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at   celser@bloomberg.net . 